         <div type="letter" xml:id="d4e38">
            <pb n="1" facs="0012_000298_000223_0001.jpg" xml:id="d4e39"/>
            <p>Memphis, May 10th 1865</p>
            <p>My Darling</p>
            <p>I arrived here <unclear reason="illegible" resp="EMS">at l.</unclear> today find business back and am at work at my desk my cold seems to be better today but last night I coughed badly. the weather is warm and I have been perspiring ever since I arrived and walked up the hill I send this to let you know of my safe arrival no time to add more</p>
            <p>Your affc Husband</p>
            <p>WRHackley</p>
         </div>
